    <!-- Section: how it works -->
      <section id="howitworks" class="head-section text-center">
        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 text-center">
            <h1 class="section-header">How it works</h1>
            <i class="fa fa-2x fa-angle-down"></i>
            <hr class="section-divider">
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-1">
            <div class="how-to">
              <h3>Add meeting participants.</h3>
              <p>ezMeeting syncs with users' Google calendars so you can have an interactive realtime display of participants' availability.
              </p>
              <img src="/img/howto1.png" class="howtopics" id="howto1"/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-3">
            <div class="how-to">
              <h3>Choose time that works for everyone.</h3>
              <p>Application will display empty timeslots when everyone is available as well as color out the slots when people are unavailable. Three customized display tabs will help you get a better sense of participants' availability so you can choose the time that works for everyone!
              </p>
              <img src="/img/howto2.png" class="howtopics" id="howto2"/>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-5">
            <div class="how-to">
              <h3>Done! Send an invitation to all participants.</h3>
              <p>When you select a time and send an invite, the application will automatically send a Google calendar invitation to all participants. The meeting will appear on your calendar as well!
              </p>
              <img src="/img/howto3.png" class="howtopics" id="howto3"/>
            <div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
